# Architecture & ADR docs

## Structure
- State **Status:** Proposed | Decided (ADR link)
- Include failure modes and degradation paths for runtime components
- Link related docs; update `docs/README.md` when adding files

## ADRs
- Irreversible or expensive choices → new `docs/decisions/NNNN-title.md`
- Do not rewrite Accepted ADRs; supersede with new number

## Diagrams
- Use Mermaid for flows; keep one diagram per major concept
- Label trust boundaries (LAN, camera, edge, server)

## Reviews
When asked to review architecture, use severity P0–P3 and cite file paths.
